{"tid":784107,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本地登革熱個案再增4宗　 爆疫源頭獅子山公園　 封場30日滅蚊","createTime":"2018-08-18T06:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T10:14:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7af8438012f8d35dde48c7a6b77c52fb6158edb","tid":784107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479124&d=n%2F1b9%2BlpRibGc%2B7vlEcTXEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=e301f36a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F20479124&h=a6d21ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180818/20479124</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月18日 <br />\n<br />\n本地登革熱個案再增4宗　<br />\n爆疫源頭獅子山公園　<br />\n封場30日滅蚊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/18la7p13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2F18la7p13.jpg&h=a14d32c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■康文署職員昨於獅子山公園入口貼封園通告。李家皓攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港昨再添4宗本地感染登革熱個案，4天累積確診11宗，追平過去4年本地個案的總和。昨日確診的3男1女患者均在潛伏期內到過疑為主要感染源頭的獅子山公園，康文署宣佈關閉公園1個月，倘稍後出現更多新個案，且與該公園相關，或延遲重開。<br />\n<br />\n記者：袁樂婷　羅繼盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新增4宗本地感染個案的患者年齡介乎40至71歲，在上周三（8日）至本周二（14日）之間發病，目前情況穩定，較早發病的3人已經退燒。衞生防護中心總監黃加慶說，4人在潛伏期內均曾到過獅子山公園，同住家人暫時沒有病徵。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a0801a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa0801a.gif&h=86cede81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9名患者曾到訪<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，至今累積的11名登革熱患者中，9人曾到該公園；餘下兩人之中，亦有1人曾到同區的黃大仙港鐵站。此外，前日確診的3宗個案已完成基因排序，結果與最早確診4宗個案的其中3宗完全一樣，即他們或有相同感染源頭。惟獨居於長洲的84歲女子，所染病毒的基因排序與其他人有別，加上在潛伏期內主要在住所附近活動，與其他人沒有共通，料從另一源頭染病。<br />\n<br />\n防治蟲鼠督導委員會昨午召開跨部門特別會議。康文署在會後宣佈，昨晚7時起關閉獅子山公園，包括棒球場和射箭場，暫定為期30日，以配合滅蚊及場地清潔，其間會噴灑蚊油、檢查溝渠有否淤塞及清理積水等，署方呼籲市民在這段時間內不要前往公園。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180818/large/a0801b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180818%2Flarge%2Fa0801b.gif&h=0841d962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食環署防治蟲鼠主任主管李明偉稱，成蚊壽命約1個月，以此為基礎決定關閉公園的時間，倘稍後陸續再有新個案，且與獅子山公園有關，或會延遲重開。他補充，白紋伊蚊的飛行距離約100米，主要在該公園活動的蚊隻，應不會飛到鄰近郊野公園的行山徑；食環署亦會在公園周邊人口較密集的地方，包括私人屋苑和公共屋邨加強滅蚊。<br />\n<br />\n黃加慶說，沒證據顯示登革熱已成風土病，期望透過滅蚊等措施遏止疫情，避免病毒在港植根。中心下周一派員到啟德社區會堂及梁顯利油麻地社區中心舉行健康講座。昨日則為獅子山公園職員進行問卷調查，有兩人報稱有病徵，10人接受抽血檢查。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n私家車落斜失控鏟菜檔3傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n「啲蚊隔住褲咬你」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「啲蚊隔住褲咬你」<br />\n<br />\n日曾關代代木公園"},{"pid":"2c23912d2d2b19bb1dc7972a52ec450fb5acca63","tid":784107,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:27:03.000Z","msg":"支持封哂全港郊野公園"},{"pid":"c4a7f452d50432fd41b3af19ea676cbd56175ad5","tid":784107,"uid":44415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"吓 香港好需要大洗牌喎<br />\n要成為風土病先啱"},{"pid":"a58f46a301d330ee68a220edec8b8bb04cf79bff","tid":784107,"uid":117584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"幾時爆鼠疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75ecac321b738be7433c02e7f514aee557e0a7f","tid":784107,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:34:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rtoLPZIajxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrtoLPZIajxw&d=n%2F1b9%2BlpRibGc%2B7vlEcTXEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=e782d93c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rtoLPZIajxw</a>"},{"pid":"379b14e0f32fff35ae44dc8eb76b543303abc818","tid":784107,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"幾時樓價跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f837764e8c4c53ff2e6ed0cf55848809857f207a","tid":784107,"uid":37539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"然後起樓？"},{"pid":"7da502974b05ce9469cc1a4838aa2a145f0836b6","tid":784107,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"公園裡面有喪屍biohazard <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba32fb929cc9ab8e2d8ee5eb4997e2e409aaa916","tid":784107,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"咬撚死d廢老"},{"pid":"d99cff524b568b26fc60c6dc8c8fbd19619c41bf","tid":784107,"uid":47205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T10:14:47.000Z","msg":"到底幾時d人先清楚係封個公園，唔係封個郊野公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}